title: Continue 10,000 $JAMM/month salary for Louis
body:
I propose that we continue to pay 10,000 $JAMM to Louis as Community Manager for Jamm. To change Louis's salary, we need an equal or higher quorum than the initial proposal: https://snapshot.page/#/jamm/proposal/QmPV4RJFXeUwuEKpYxcJ2uPgpS9ao3aE3XBGMxR9HvLGcS.
